According to the given screen image status, in order to complete the subtask "Click somewhere else or select the Select tool to complete the drawing", we can perform a simple mouse click action in the blank area of the document, which will cancel the current drawing selection. The following operation commands are in JSON format:```json
[
    {"action_type": "MouseAction", "mouse_action_type": "click", "mouse_button": "left", "mouse_position": {"width": 224, "height": 252}}
]
```In this operation, I choose to click a point (about 200 in width and 200 in height) in the blank area of the document to ensure that the circle is drawn and no longer in editing status.
